On Wednesday, September 10, 2008,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        EXTENDED HUMAN CORPORATION by 
                        Mulay, James, Odessa 33556.
                        The USPTO has given the EXTENDED HUMAN CORPORATION 
                        trademark serial  number of  77567151.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - FAILURE TO RESPOND OR LATE RESPONSE.
                        The correspondent listed for EXTENDED HUMAN CORPORATION is 
                        
                        
                                            MULAY, JAMES of 
                                            6521 THOROUGHBRED LOOP,  ODESSA, FL 33556-1858,  
                                .
